\c 24 Jobho haanzwisisi kuti vatadzi vanoregereiko kurohwa
\v1 WaMasimbaose anoregereiko kutara nguva dzokutonga? Vanomuziva vanoregereiko kuona mazuva ake? 2 Vanoshandura miganho varipo; Vanopamba mapoka amakwai, vachiafudza. 3 Vanotinha mbongoro yenherera, Vanotora nzombe yechirikadzi vachiita rubatso. 4 Vanodzinga varombo panzira; Varombo venyika vanovanda vose. 5 Tarira, sembizi murenje Vanobudira kumabasa avo, vachishingairira zvokwadi; Renje rinovapa zvokudya zvavana vavo. 6 Vanocheka zvavanodya kusango; Vanounganidza madzambiringa avakaipa. 7 Vanovata usiku hwose vasina zvavakafuka,
\s Pachando havana
\s chavangazvifukidza nacho.
\p
\v 8 Vakanyorova nokupfunha
\s kwemvura yamakomo, Vanombundikira dombo
\s nokushaiwa pokutizira.
\p
\v 9 Varipo vanobvuta nherera pazamu ramai,
\p Nokutora rubatso rwavarombo;
\v 1 ° Naizvozvo vanofamba vasina zvavakafuka,
\s Vanotakura zvisote vane nzara;
\p
\v 11 Vanosvina mafuta mukati
\s mamasvingo avanhu ava; Vanotsika zvisviniro zvamadzambiringa avo, vachifa
\s nenyota.
\p
\v 12 Vanhu vanogomera mukati meguta rina vanhu vazhinji,
\s Uye mweya yavakakuvadzwa inochema;
\s Kunyange zvakadaro Mwari haane hanya
\s nezvisina kururama.
\p
\v 13 Ndivo vanovenga chiedza; Havazivi nzira dzacho,
\s Havarambi vachifamba pamakwara acho.
\p
\v 14 Muurayi anomuka kana kwoedza, anouraya murombo neanoshaiwa; Usiku wakafanana nomubi.
\p
\v 15 Ziso remhombwewo rinomirira rubvunzavaeni,
\s Achiti, "Hakune ziso richandiona;" Ndokufukidza chiso chake.
\p
\v 16 Usiku vanopaza dzimba;
\s Masikati vanozvipfigira;
\s Havazivi chiedza.
\p
\v 17 Nokuti mangwanani akaita serima guru kwavari vose;
\s Nokuti vanoziva kutyisa kwerima guru.
\p
\v 18 Iye anofambisa pamusoro pemvura; Mugove wavo wakatukwa panyika; Haachafambi nenzira yeminda
\s yemidzambiringa.
\p
\v 19 Kuoma nokupisa kunopedza mvura yechando;
\s Ndizvo zvinoita Sheori navakatadza.
\p
\v 20 Chizvaro chichamukanganwa; honye dzichatapirirwa naye;
\p UnCIND.
\v 6 ny‘gariv,ir,
\s Uye kusarurama kuchavhunwa somuti.
\p
\v 21 Iye unoparadza han'a isingabereki; Haaitiri chirikadzi zvakanaka.
\p
\v 22 Anobvisa vane simba nesimba rake; Kana iye achisimuka, hakuna munhu
\s anoziva kana achararama.
\p
\v 23 Mwari anovagarisa vakachengetwa, vachivimba nazvo;
\s Asi meso ake anotarira nzira dzavo.
\p
\v 24 Vanokudzwa; gare-gare vaenda; Vanodukupiswa, vanobviswa
\s panzira savamwe vose, Vanochekwa semisoro yehura
\s dzezviyo.
\p
\v 25 Kana zvisina kudaro zvino, ndiani angati ndine nhema,
\s Nokushaisha mashoko angu simba here?
